                <h2>Recruitment Marketing and Employer Branding</h2>
            </header>
            <article class="description">
                <p>You may have a great business built on a novel idea, but you still need passionate and talented people to help you succeed. From Software Developers to Sales Reps and CEOs, I have developed comprehensive marketing strategies for attracting, engaging and retaining quality talent to a variety of organizations, including Flight Centre. With a focus on employer brand and EVP development, I’ve created compelling content and effective advertising for attracting Band Managers in British Columbia, Engineers in Alberta, Instructors in Nunavut and more. In 2015, I was the Top Global Recruitment Marketing Specialist at Employment Office.</p>
                <p>Whether you need assistance with market research, job analysis, copywriting and content creation, digital or print advertising, video production or social media management, I can help you formulate an effective strategy for talent attraction.</p>
